data.description: Welcome to your own slice of paradise! This 1-story pool home sits on half an acre of landscaped grounds, offering tranquility, comfort, and ample space. With 6 beds 2 of which are suites, 3 baths, and over 2,500 sq ft, this home impresses. Step inside to a spacious and inviting layout. The chef's kitchen features a breakfast bar and granite countertops with tons of space, and stainless appliances and is open to a large dining room perfect for hosting the whole family. The adjacent living area boasts a cozy fireplace, creating a warm atmosphere. The pool area is a serene retreat, perfect for relaxation. Enjoy a dip in the pool or bask in the Florida sunshine. The seamless flow between indoor and outdoor spaces makes entertaining a breeze. Situated on half an acre, this home offers ample outdoor space. Recent updates include roof replaced 2017, water heater 2017, water system and water softner 2023, and variable speed pool pump 2023.
